short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Spam Google Forms and Microsoft Forms like a champ

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
You can use this extension to submit Google Forms and Microsoft Forms multiple times. You only need to fill the form once and fill in how many times you want to submit the form. This extension will be activated only for official Google Forms and Microsoft Forms.

✨ Submit Google Forms and Microsoft Forms multiple times with one click

🌎Google Forms features🌎
✨ Unlimited submissions (Premium)
✨ Control spamming speed (Premium)
✨ Randomizer (Premium)
✨ Submit form that require sign-in (Premium)

What's new?

💚 Randomizer now works for Rating on Google Forms!
💚 Borang now supports Microsoft Forms!
🐛 Bug fix: Empty response submitted for form that has no "required" question
